			>
			<DIV>The problem with factoring in Defensive like that is that the mobs in single group content rarely, if ever, last 3 minutes. This creates a somewhat inaccurate picture as unless the tank is facing the mobs in rapid order,&nbsp;(up to 6 if the fights are 30 seconds each),&nbsp;with no gap between contact, they will not get the full use of Defensive.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I really have some serrious doubts as to the accuracy of including such Disciplines into the equation, it's clear these were not designed for today's single group content or else they would have a more compatible duration and refresh.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Which leads to a&nbsp;question to ask Warriors, do they use these Discs in this manner, popping Defensive and Evasive when they refresh? Which is also a huge factor to consider when making such comparisons otherwise your just pen and paper theory that doesn't actually apply to the game.</DIV>	
